    <para>
      To download the needed files using <xref linkend='wget'/>,
      use the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir app &amp;&amp;
cd app &amp;&amp;
grep -v '^#' ../app-&xorg-version;-list | wget -i- -c \
    -B &xorg-download-http;/app/</userinput></screen>

